Vendor: Kichler
Type: Path Lights
Price: 189.99

2700K Textured Black Fundamentals 21 LED Path Light

Basic, uncomplicated design for maximum versatility, Energy Efficient.

Features:

  • Cast brass or aluminum construction
  • 8 integrated high output Nichia® LEDs
  • Coordinates with the 16110 deck light
  • Includes an 8" ground stake for installation into soil
  • Operates between 9V and 15V with no loss in output due to constant current technology
  • Note: Brass will develop a natural patina over time
  • ETL listed for wet locations

Dimensions:

  • Height: 21"
  • Width: 6"

Electrical Specifications:

  • Bulb Type: LED
  • Bulb Socket Type: N/A (Integrated LED)
  • Wattage: 4.3
  • Color Temperature: 2700K (Warm White)
  • Lumen Output: 294
  • CRI (Color Rendering Index): 80
  • Average LED Life: 40,000 hours
  • Voltage: 12 (Low Voltage)
  • Amp Draw: 5.8 VA
  • See the attached spec sheets and catalog pages for full photometric details

Compatible Accessories:

  • For surface mounting, purchase the 15601 or 15607 mounting bracket
